\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/8.8-10,14?lang=por#p8\">3 Né. 8:8–10, 14</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"13\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note13a\" data-full-marker=\"13a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124151194\" id=\"note13a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/10.12?lang=por#p12\">3 Né. 10:12</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note13b\" data-full-marker=\"13b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124151196\" id=\"note13b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/jer/3.22?lang=por#p22\">Jer. 3:22</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.32?lang=por#p32\">3 Né. 18:32</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"14\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note14a\" data-full-marker=\"14a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124151198\" id=\"note14a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.24-28?lang=por#p24\">2 Né. 26:24–28</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.33-36?lang=por#p33\">Al. 5:33–36</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note14b\" data-full-marker=\"14b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124151200\" id=\"note14b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/john/3.16?lang=por#p16\">Jo. 3:16</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note14c\" data-full-marker=\"14c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124151202\" id=\"note14c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/19.36?lang=por#p36\">Al. 19:36</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"15\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note15a\" data-full-marker=\"15a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124151204\" id=\"note15a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/john/1.1-3?lang=por#p1\">Jo. 1:1–3</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/col/1.16?lang=por#p16\">Col. 1:16</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/st